WorkItem.Description: I have the Polished Dragonslayer's Signet (Onyxia head quest reward) marked as available to the Optimizer in the Shadow Priest module. When I run the Optimizer, it has me equipping the ring in both ring slots. While the ring is NOT explicitly labeled as unique, one can only complete the quest once; having two of these rings is impossible.
WorkItem.Summary: [Optimizer] Attempting to equip two Polished Dragonslayer's Signets

Comments.Message: Edit item, set the item as Unique. Yeah I know it seems silly, but as you said yourself, its just not explicitly labeled as unique, but you can only complete quest once.
